1
00:00:04,390 --> 00:00:05,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you looking at?</font>

2
00:00:06,520 --> 00:00:10,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This says they can send us 
a few on a trial basis.</font>

3
00:00:10,300 --> 00:00:12,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't wait to see what they send.</font>

4
00:00:12,560 --> 00:00:14,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't let Bel-san take advantage of you.</font>

5
00:00:14,980 --> 00:00:15,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

6
00:00:15,980 --> 00:00:19,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She'll send over some 
ridiculously expensive devices.</font>

7
00:00:19,260 --> 00:00:21,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that what this is?</font>

8
00:00:21,170 --> 00:00:23,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course, her main objective is...</font>

9
00:00:23,920 --> 00:00:26,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right? Isn't the shape 
of it just wonderful?</font>

10
00:00:26,640 --> 00:00:30,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You absolutely must see and touch 
and experience it for yourself!</font>

11
00:00:31,250 --> 00:00:36,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She just wants to show you all 
the torture devices she likes.</font>

12
00:00:36,440 --> 00:00:38,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

13
00:02:02,100 --> 00:02:06,180
<font size="20" color="#000000">{\an8}<b><font size="35"><font color="#171719">The <font color="#d9000d">Daily <font color="#269df2">L<font color="#171719">ife of a <font color="#ef670f">P<font color="#171719">art-Time <font color="#44c10c">T<font color="#171719">orturer</font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></b></font>

14
00:02:14,360 --> 00:02:16,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm finished with intake.</font>

15
00:02:16,050 --> 00:02:19,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, good work. You can go now.</font>

16
00:02:22,370 --> 00:02:24,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! We have a wild rabbit!</font>

17
00:02:24,560 --> 00:02:26,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? A wild rabbit?</font>

18
00:02:26,520 --> 00:02:28,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What an adorable name.</font>

19
00:02:31,040 --> 00:02:33,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wild rabbit?</font>

20
00:02:34,470 --> 00:02:35,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So many spikes.</font>

21
00:02:36,380 --> 00:02:39,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How is this used?</font>

22
00:02:39,210 --> 00:02:44,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After you... tie them to the wheel,</font>

23
00:02:44,890 --> 00:02:46,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you turn this...</font>

24
00:02:47,140 --> 00:02:50,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and the spikes on the bottom 
gradually strip off their skin.</font>

25
00:02:51,080 --> 00:02:54,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's like using a grater 
over their entire body.</font>

26
00:02:54,570 --> 00:02:58,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The handle's hard to move, 
so it's hard to gauge the tolerances.</font>

27
00:02:59,000 --> 00:03:01,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Won't they die?</font>

28
00:03:01,190 --> 00:03:03,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They last longer than you'd think. 
It gets messy, though.</font>

29
00:03:06,670 --> 00:03:09,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">These are small, but they're spiky, too!</font>

30
00:03:09,230 --> 00:03:11,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They look a little like accessories.</font>

31
00:03:14,850 --> 00:03:17,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no point in using 
that on your skinny neck.</font>

32
00:03:17,840 --> 00:03:19,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

33
00:03:19,630 --> 00:03:21,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's adorable.</i></font>

34
00:03:21,310 --> 00:03:23,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It reeks of iron.</font>

35
00:03:25,500 --> 00:03:27,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This one isn't spiky!</font>

36
00:03:27,600 --> 00:03:31,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a cage to hang people in and 
expose them to the elements, right?</font>

37
00:03:31,440 --> 00:03:34,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But do you just lock them in there?</font>

38
00:03:34,490 --> 00:03:35,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No.</font>

39
00:03:35,880 --> 00:03:38,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They can't sit or anything, 
so it's pretty rough.</font>

40
00:03:38,790 --> 00:03:40,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a battle of attrition.</font>

41
00:03:40,280 --> 00:03:42,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd rather not be on the 
giving or the receiving end.</font>

42
00:03:42,400 --> 00:03:43,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Me neither.</font>

43
00:03:44,990 --> 00:03:47,950
<font size="20" color="#000000"><font size="35"><b>

44
00:03:48,160 --> 00:03:50,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's adorable.</i></font></b></font></font>

45
00:03:50,140 --> 00:03:52,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's more comfortable than you'd think.</font>

46
00:03:53,560 --> 00:03:55,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Were there any that interested you?</font>

47
00:03:55,920 --> 00:03:58,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's one that's deeply intriguing,</font>

48
00:03:58,480 --> 00:04:01,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but it's large, so it may 
be a little inconvenient.</font>

49
00:04:01,240 --> 00:04:07,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Most of the big ones tend to lean 
toward long battles or heavy damage.</font>

50
00:04:07,490 --> 00:04:11,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're interesting, but they might 
not be suited to our daily work.</font>

51
00:04:11,180 --> 00:04:12,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right?</font>

52
00:04:12,580 --> 00:04:15,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, wait! Please let me out of here!</font>

53
00:04:13,050 --> 00:04:14,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's true.</font>

54
00:04:16,020 --> 00:04:18,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're adorable, so I thought 
I'd keep you here as a pet.</font>

55
00:04:19,280 --> 00:04:22,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please don't say that with an expression 
that looks like you mean it!</font>

56
00:04:24,770 --> 00:04:27,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, so we'll return all of them.</font>

57
00:04:27,540 --> 00:04:29,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

58
00:04:29,500 --> 00:04:31,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She'll probably come to 
pick them up tomorrow,</font>

59
00:04:31,900 --> 00:04:33,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so we can leave them there and go home.</font>

60
00:04:36,050 --> 00:04:40,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is hard to use, 
but it does have a lot of impact.</font>

61
00:04:40,300 --> 00:04:43,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Starting the fear through visuals 
is highly effective, isn't it?</font>

62
00:04:43,820 --> 00:04:47,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe this piece places more 
importance on that than usability.</font>

63
00:04:47,520 --> 00:04:48,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

64
00:04:48,630 --> 00:04:52,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The kinds of devices that 
inspire fear are actually...</font>

65
00:04:53,260 --> 00:04:56,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, it's nice that they seem 
to have learned something.</font>

66
00:04:56,450 --> 00:04:59,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Belta can be helpful 
every once in a while.</font>

67
00:05:01,800 --> 00:05:03,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes? Hello.</font>

68
00:05:03,940 --> 00:05:05,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Hi, Bel-san.</i></font>

69
00:05:05,630 --> 00:05:09,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Sorry, but we'll be returning all 
the equipment you sent over.</i></font>

70
00:05:09,440 --> 00:05:10,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

71
00:05:10,560 --> 00:05:12,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They're not very practical.</i></font>

72
00:05:12,580 --> 00:05:13,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hang on!</font>

73
00:05:13,770 --> 00:05:15,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There are uses for them 
other than torture, you know!</font>

74
00:05:15,290 --> 00:05:16,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There are uses for them 
other than torture, you know!</i></font>

75
00:05:16,400 --> 00:05:18,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Don't they make great 
interior decoration?</i></font>

76
00:05:18,500 --> 00:05:21,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>All those cold, spiky, magnificent forms!</i></font>

77
00:05:21,020 --> 00:05:24,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Just thinking about the sight of them, 
all made to hurt people,</i></font>

78
00:05:24,160 --> 00:05:26,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">even the karma that 
casts its shadow over—</font>

79
00:05:29,160 --> 00:05:33,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've heard that Belta-san actually
does live with torture devices.</font>

80
00:05:33,070 --> 00:05:34,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow.</font>

81
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:42,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">'Sup?</font>

82
00:05:42,490 --> 00:05:43,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sero-san?!</font>

83
00:05:43,950 --> 00:05:46,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What happened? Why are you injured?</font>

84
00:05:46,480 --> 00:05:48,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shouldn't you take the day off?</font>

85
00:05:48,720 --> 00:05:50,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm fine.</font>

86
00:05:50,200 --> 00:05:52,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not as bad as it looks.</font>

87
00:05:52,650 --> 00:05:54,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Was it a traffic accident or something?</font>

88
00:05:54,850 --> 00:05:58,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, no. This was just your average...</font>

89
00:05:58,880 --> 00:05:59,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">attack.</font>

90
00:06:00,130 --> 00:06:01,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Attack?!</font>

91
00:06:01,580 --> 00:06:04,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Some dangerous compatriots 
of someone I tortured before.</font>

92
00:06:05,200 --> 00:06:07,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess it's what you'd call... 
"paying respects."</font>

93
00:06:07,930 --> 00:06:09,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You say that like it's normal.</font>

94
00:06:09,560 --> 00:06:12,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I <i>am</i> famous in the industry.</font>

95
00:06:16,610 --> 00:06:20,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, so first I got hit with a 
metal pipe out of nowhere...</font>

96
00:06:20,840 --> 00:06:21,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

97
00:06:22,870 --> 00:06:25,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then I went in with a headbutt.</font>

98
00:06:27,310 --> 00:06:29,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And then, I called the police.</font>

99
00:06:29,790 --> 00:06:31,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's all too wild for me.</font>

100
00:06:33,260 --> 00:06:35,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And, well, looking like this,</font>

101
00:06:35,840 --> 00:06:38,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">my torture targets 
wouldn't take me seriously.</font>

102
00:06:38,490 --> 00:06:40,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I'll take a supportive role today.</font>

103
00:06:40,740 --> 00:06:44,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sheesh. Just don't push 
yourself too hard, okay?</font>

104
00:06:44,010 --> 00:06:45,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, I won't.</font>

105
00:06:51,080 --> 00:06:54,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This case... That's already next week.</i></font>

106
00:06:54,180 --> 00:06:58,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Then... I'll have Mike take that, and...</i></font>

107
00:06:58,800 --> 00:07:00,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I guess I'll give this one to Hugh.</i></font>

108
00:07:05,010 --> 00:07:07,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">About next week's schedule...</font>

109
00:07:07,520 --> 00:07:11,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would you rather do 
this one or this... one?</font>

110
00:07:14,340 --> 00:07:16,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Huh? He's ignoring me?</i></font>

111
00:07:17,360 --> 00:07:18,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey!</font>

112
00:07:18,740 --> 00:07:19,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Siu-san!</font>

113
00:07:19,480 --> 00:07:21,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's going on?</font>

114
00:07:21,680 --> 00:07:24,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those injuries you have.</font>

115
00:07:24,190 --> 00:07:24,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

116
00:07:25,670 --> 00:07:27,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you okay?</font>

117
00:07:27,080 --> 00:07:29,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm totally fine!</font>

118
00:07:29,440 --> 00:07:32,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I went to the hospital, and they 
went overboard with the bandages.</font>

119
00:07:32,780 --> 00:07:34,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is nothing!</font>

120
00:07:36,600 --> 00:07:38,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are you smiling?</font>

121
00:07:38,720 --> 00:07:40,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After going off on your own...</font>

122
00:07:41,300 --> 00:07:43,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The torture session that got you attacked</font>

123
00:07:43,870 --> 00:07:46,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">was one that I was 
supposed to handle, wasn't it?</font>

124
00:07:46,360 --> 00:07:48,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, but switching cases isn't—</font>

125
00:07:48,340 --> 00:07:50,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's what landed you in that state.</font>

126
00:07:50,570 --> 00:07:53,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And if it is... so what?!</font>

127
00:07:56,200 --> 00:08:00,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why do you always try to 
take on everything by yourself?</font>

128
00:08:02,400 --> 00:08:05,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have so much that 
you have to protect as it is!</font>

129
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:10,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please don't include me in that group.</font>

130
00:08:11,930 --> 00:08:14,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If anything happened to you, 
it'd be a problem.</font>

131
00:08:14,760 --> 00:08:16,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For this job, for everyone...</font>

132
00:08:16,610 --> 00:08:18,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, it causes problems for me</font>

133
00:08:18,640 --> 00:08:21,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">if you're not strong and healthy!</font>

134
00:08:21,760 --> 00:08:24,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And it's not just me.</font>

135
00:08:25,180 --> 00:08:26,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You seem pretty angry.</font>

136
00:08:28,740 --> 00:08:30,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What about you?</font>

137
00:08:31,700 --> 00:08:33,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You were angry for my sake, right?</font>

138
00:08:34,540 --> 00:08:37,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then please understand 
why I'm angry, too!</font>

139
00:08:40,800 --> 00:08:44,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For me, the idea of you getting hurt...</font>

140
00:08:44,670 --> 00:08:47,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">of the people you love getting hurt...</font>

141
00:08:48,040 --> 00:08:49,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't want that.</font>

142
00:08:50,600 --> 00:08:52,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If the alternative is you 
taking on everything alone,</font>

143
00:08:53,400 --> 00:08:55,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd rather get injured!</font>

144
00:08:59,390 --> 00:09:03,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm more useful than I used to be, right?</font>

145
00:09:04,520 --> 00:09:08,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So let me take on just a little bit...</font>

146
00:09:10,550 --> 00:09:13,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">of everything you're carrying.</font>

147
00:09:17,280 --> 00:09:18,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ow!</font>

148
00:09:18,960 --> 00:09:19,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Moron.</font>

149
00:09:22,260 --> 00:09:24,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you drop it, there'll 
be no forgiveness.</font>

150
00:09:29,600 --> 00:09:32,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't drop it even if it kills me!</font>

151
00:09:32,040 --> 00:09:34,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If it kills you, huh?</font>

152
00:09:34,360 --> 00:09:36,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There you go, talking big again.</font>

153
00:09:36,940 --> 00:09:38,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! Are you doubting me?</font>

154
00:09:39,080 --> 00:09:42,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm serious! And I'll prove it to you.</font>

155
00:09:43,500 --> 00:09:45,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't go along with this.</font>

156
00:09:45,440 --> 00:09:47,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, you're the one who said it.</font>

157
00:09:47,540 --> 00:09:49,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just make sure you watch me work, okay?</font>

158
00:09:49,780 --> 00:09:51,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a pain.</font>

159
00:09:52,980 --> 00:09:55,990
<font size="20" color="#000000">{\an8}<b><font size="35"><font color="#fefefe">The <font color="#4bd12d">D<font color="#fefefe">aily <font color="#eda32a">L<font color="#fefefe">ife of a <font color="#ca003d">P<font color="#fefefe">art-Time <font color="#2761d5">T<font color="#fefefe">orturer</font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></b></font>

160
00:09:55,990 --> 00:09:58,990
<font size="20" color="#000000">{\an8}<b><font size="35"><font color="#0b0a0c">The <font color="#3067de">D<font color="#0b0a0c">aily <font color="#cc0642">L<font color="#0b0a0c">ife of a <font color="#eea731">P<font color="#0b0a0c">art-Time <font color="#55d339">T<font color="#0b0a0c">orturer</font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></b></font>

161
00:10:05,000 --> 00:10:07,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is amazing! It's so pretty!</font>

162
00:10:07,900 --> 00:10:10,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All of you are always 
working so hard for us.</font>

163
00:10:10,850 --> 00:10:12,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought it'd be nice for a change.</font>

164
00:10:13,370 --> 00:10:16,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, right. Where are 
Leu-chan and Nero-chan?</font>

165
00:10:16,340 --> 00:10:18,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't need to be 
considerate on our accounts.</font>

166
00:10:18,640 --> 00:10:19,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Moron.</font>

167
00:10:19,830 --> 00:10:21,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who would bother being 
considerate of you?</font>

168
00:10:22,480 --> 00:10:24,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I let my brother and his wife 
take them out, that's all.</font>

169
00:10:25,540 --> 00:10:26,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Papa!</font>

170
00:10:26,520 --> 00:10:29,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eri-kun said they'll 
take us to Lulupii Land!</font>

171
00:10:27,890 --> 00:10:34,270
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font face="Comic Sans MS">{\an7}<font size="25"><font color="#252127">Lulupii</font></font></font></b></font>

172
00:10:29,970 --> 00:10:31,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And that we can stay over!</font>

173
00:10:31,070 --> 00:10:33,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you can go to the hot springs!</font>

174
00:10:34,500 --> 00:10:35,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, my.</font>

175
00:10:36,740 --> 00:10:38,570
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font face="Georgia"><font size="25"><font color="#2e211c">Iris Room</font></font></font></b></font>

176
00:10:37,520 --> 00:10:38,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay...</font>

177
00:10:38,570 --> 00:10:41,280
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font size="15"><font color="#000000">Sharing 
a Room</font></font></b></font>

178
00:10:38,810 --> 00:10:41,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're free until dinnertime.</font>

179
00:10:41,280 --> 00:10:42,740
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font face="Georgia"><font size="25"><font color="#2e211c">Sakura Room</font></font></font></b></font>

180
00:10:41,460 --> 00:10:42,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay!</font>

181
00:10:42,740 --> 00:10:44,450
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font size="15"><font color="#000000">Sharing 
a Room</font></font></b></font>

182
00:10:42,980 --> 00:10:44,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Understood.</font>

183
00:10:44,450 --> 00:10:47,910
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font face="Georgia"><font size="25"><font color="#2e211c">Peony Room</font></font></font></b></font>

184
00:10:44,720 --> 00:10:46,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Should we hit the
 baths before dinner?</font>

185
00:10:46,870 --> 00:10:47,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

186
00:10:49,050 --> 00:10:50,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

187
00:10:50,130 --> 00:10:53,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't these pairings mean I'm the 
only one who doesn't get to relax?</font>

188
00:10:53,190 --> 00:10:54,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure you will.</font>

189
00:10:53,190 --> 00:10:54,630
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font size="15"><font color="#000000">Sharing 
a Room</font></font></b></font>

190
00:10:54,640 --> 00:10:56,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm a comforting guy, you know.</font>

191
00:10:56,520 --> 00:10:58,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's news to me.</font>

192
00:11:05,460 --> 00:11:08,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is paradise.</font>

193
00:11:08,410 --> 00:11:09,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right?</font>

194
00:11:10,230 --> 00:11:12,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It feels so good,</font>

195
00:11:12,120 --> 00:11:15,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it's strange to think that if you used it
a little differently, it could be torture.</font>

196
00:11:15,640 --> 00:11:18,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You mean like a water chamber 
or a boiling cauldron?</font>

197
00:11:18,100 --> 00:11:19,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, exactly!</font>

198
00:11:20,330 --> 00:11:21,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sero-san!</font>

199
00:11:23,030 --> 00:11:26,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We don't do either of those 
at our place, right?</font>

200
00:11:26,490 --> 00:11:29,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If they get stubborn, it's a pain 
to figure out the tolerances.</font>

201
00:11:29,290 --> 00:11:31,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You could say it's not cost-effective.</font>

202
00:11:31,660 --> 00:11:32,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Besides...</font>

203
00:11:33,460 --> 00:11:37,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">using huge amounts of water 
isn't very eco-friendly.</font>

204
00:11:37,230 --> 00:11:41,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Spirytus is a torture firm 
that's kind to the planet.</font>

205
00:11:41,010 --> 00:11:42,970
<font size="20" color="#000000"><font face="Times New Roman"><b>{\an7}<font color="#de4a5b">Torture <font color="#4b4b4b">builds a sustainable society</font></font></b></font></font>

206
00:11:41,010 --> 00:11:42,970
<font size="20" color="#000000"><font face="Times New Roman"><b>{\an8}<font color="#de4a5b">Give the villains 
the <font color="#9a4f59">iron hammer</font></font></b></font></font>

207
00:11:47,180 --> 00:11:50,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now that I think about it, 
Hera-san and Noe-san haven't come yet.</font>

208
00:11:51,950 --> 00:11:53,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh.</font>

209
00:11:53,110 --> 00:11:55,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're probably relaxing 
in a private bath.</font>

210
00:11:55,660 --> 00:11:58,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Despite how they seem, 
they're both shy.</font>

211
00:11:58,390 --> 00:12:01,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I-I didn't realize.</font>

212
00:12:05,990 --> 00:12:08,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're quite the smooth talker.</font>

213
00:12:08,500 --> 00:12:11,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, it's not my place to say anything.</font>

214
00:12:12,030 --> 00:12:14,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's the kind of thing 
you say when you want to,</font>

215
00:12:14,180 --> 00:12:16,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to the person you want to, right?</font>

216
00:12:17,770 --> 00:12:20,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm ready to listen anytime, so...</font>

217
00:12:20,230 --> 00:12:21,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, yeah.</font>

218
00:12:21,520 --> 00:12:24,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll be here year round, 
no breaks, twenty-four hours a day.</font>

219
00:12:25,780 --> 00:12:27,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How considerate of you.</font>

220
00:12:28,850 --> 00:12:30,810
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font face="Georgia"><font size="25"><font color="#2e211c">Iris Room</font></font></font></b></font>

221
00:12:36,170 --> 00:12:38,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see the scars have faded quite a bit.</font>

222
00:12:39,420 --> 00:12:41,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have they?</font>

223
00:12:42,200 --> 00:12:44,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is a rare chance.</font>

224
00:12:44,420 --> 00:12:46,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you sure you don't 
want to be with everyone?</font>

225
00:12:48,520 --> 00:12:51,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those boys won't say anything about it.</font>

226
00:12:52,160 --> 00:12:54,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't think they would.</font>

227
00:12:56,220 --> 00:12:57,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's just that I...</font>

228
00:12:58,150 --> 00:13:00,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just want to be with you, Hera-san.</font>

229
00:13:01,350 --> 00:13:02,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In that case...</font>

230
00:13:02,800 --> 00:13:06,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's been a while. Maybe I'll ask 
you to wash my back for me.</font>

231
00:13:06,030 --> 00:13:08,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course! Just leave it to me!</font>

232
00:13:12,520 --> 00:13:14,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, all done!</font>

233
00:13:15,210 --> 00:13:17,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've always wondered...</font>

234
00:13:18,220 --> 00:13:22,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sero-san, why do you 
always dry his hair for him?</font>

235
00:13:22,890 --> 00:13:24,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh.</font>

236
00:13:24,040 --> 00:13:26,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Since it's long, it's faster 
if I dry it for him.</font>

237
00:13:27,370 --> 00:13:30,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Plus, over all the times 
he's let me do it,</font>

238
00:13:31,030 --> 00:13:33,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've gotten pretty fond of his hair.</font>

239
00:13:33,970 --> 00:13:35,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's so creepy.</i></font>

240
00:13:37,610 --> 00:13:39,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Frankly, it's a pain,</font>

241
00:13:39,080 --> 00:13:42,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but if I don't dry it right, 
he starts nagging me.</font>

242
00:13:43,580 --> 00:13:47,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And, I mean, he's not bad at it, 
so if he wants to do it that badly,</font>

243
00:13:47,480 --> 00:13:50,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I figure I'll just let 
him do what he wants.</font>

244
00:13:50,360 --> 00:13:52,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seriously, though, it's a pain.</font>

245
00:13:52,510 --> 00:13:55,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's salon-level service!</i></font>

246
00:13:56,060 --> 00:13:58,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There, Siu-san. You're all done.</font>

247
00:13:58,890 --> 00:13:59,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right.</font>

248
00:14:04,830 --> 00:14:07,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks for all your work, everyone!</font>

249
00:14:07,890 --> 00:14:09,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cheers!</font>

250
00:14:09,680 --> 00:14:11,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cheers!</font>

251
00:14:12,670 --> 00:14:14,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Siu-san, have some more.</font>

252
00:14:14,410 --> 00:14:15,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure.</font>

253
00:14:15,680 --> 00:14:17,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you eating, Noe?</font>

254
00:14:17,830 --> 00:14:20,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't need you to remind me. I am.</font>

255
00:14:21,080 --> 00:14:24,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have you gone on company 
trips like this before?</font>

256
00:14:24,510 --> 00:14:25,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

257
00:14:25,540 --> 00:14:26,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One time,</font>

258
00:14:26,640 --> 00:14:30,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sero and Noe got all worked up 
and had a table tennis match.</font>

259
00:14:30,370 --> 00:14:31,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right.</font>

260
00:14:31,830 --> 00:14:34,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We had to keep them company 
until they got sleepy.</font>

261
00:14:34,420 --> 00:14:37,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really? So, who won?</font>

262
00:14:37,640 --> 00:14:40,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which of us was it? 
I'm pretty sure it was me.</font>

263
00:14:40,520 --> 00:14:42,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think it was me.</font>

264
00:14:42,010 --> 00:14:43,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't remember?</font>

265
00:14:46,140 --> 00:14:47,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now that I think about it...</font>

266
00:14:48,110 --> 00:14:53,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mike and Hugh are the first ones in 
a long time to stick around this long.</font>

267
00:14:53,420 --> 00:14:55,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That makes me happy somehow.</font>

268
00:14:55,980 --> 00:14:58,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe I'll make this my primary job.</font>

269
00:14:58,090 --> 00:14:59,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just kidding!</font>

270
00:14:59,520 --> 00:15:02,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're welcome here anytime!</font>

271
00:15:02,520 --> 00:15:05,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What about you, Hugh? Do you have 
a lot of future career plans?</font>

272
00:15:06,320 --> 00:15:08,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I... suppose so.</font>

273
00:15:08,900 --> 00:15:12,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm still thinking 
about what I want to do,</font>

274
00:15:12,510 --> 00:15:17,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but my parents are supportive of my 
being involved with torture in the future.</font>

275
00:15:17,800 --> 00:15:20,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a wonderful family.</font>

276
00:15:22,850 --> 00:15:24,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When we grow up...</font>

277
00:15:24,480 --> 00:15:26,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">...we'll do the same job as you, Papa!</font>

278
00:15:26,620 --> 00:15:27,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't.</font>

279
00:15:27,710 --> 00:15:29,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But why?</font>

280
00:15:31,480 --> 00:15:33,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Should I learn from their example?</font>

281
00:15:33,120 --> 00:15:36,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They have their rules, you have yours. 
Don't let yourself lose heart!</font>

282
00:15:39,770 --> 00:15:42,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! Who gave Noe alcohol?!</font>

283
00:15:42,670 --> 00:15:44,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I poured it for him!</font>

284
00:15:44,370 --> 00:15:45,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You idiot!</font>

285
00:15:45,840 --> 00:15:48,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When he gets drunk, 
he's more of a pain than I am!</font>

286
00:15:48,600 --> 00:15:51,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So he's aware that he's a pain.</i></font>

287
00:15:52,350 --> 00:15:54,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm no good at all.</font>

288
00:15:54,850 --> 00:15:56,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have to contribute 
more to the company...</font>

289
00:15:56,830 --> 00:16:00,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not true! 
You're a huge help to us!</font>

290
00:16:00,140 --> 00:16:03,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But someone like me will never...</font>

291
00:16:02,600 --> 00:16:05,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I'm telling you, you're 
already working hard enough!</font>

292
00:16:04,280 --> 00:16:05,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Hilarious.</i></font>

293
00:16:05,370 --> 00:16:06,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Adorable.</i></font>

294
00:16:06,480 --> 00:16:07,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait!</font>

295
00:16:07,000 --> 00:16:09,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are you grabbing snacks 
to have with your drinks?!</font>

296
00:16:13,180 --> 00:16:15,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Man, I sure drank a lot.</font>

297
00:16:16,590 --> 00:16:18,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't fall, now.</font>

298
00:16:18,830 --> 00:16:21,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who'd be clumsy enough to...</font>

299
00:16:23,040 --> 00:16:24,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you all right?</font>

300
00:16:26,640 --> 00:16:28,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I told you so!</font>

301
00:16:28,760 --> 00:16:31,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Be careful, okay?</font>

302
00:16:32,880 --> 00:16:35,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry, Hera-san.</font>

303
00:16:35,100 --> 00:16:36,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Moron! Idiot!</font>

304
00:16:36,280 --> 00:16:38,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}They make a ruckus 
no matter where they go.</font>

305
00:16:36,630 --> 00:16:38,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What did you just say?</font>

306
00:16:41,360 --> 00:16:42,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ow!</font>

307
00:16:43,490 --> 00:16:45,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry. I didn't notice you were there.</font>

308
00:16:45,320 --> 00:16:46,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you okay?</font>

309
00:16:46,800 --> 00:16:49,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, no. I should have been more careful.</font>

310
00:16:49,220 --> 00:16:51,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My cheeks are bouncy, so I'm just fine!</font>

311
00:16:53,440 --> 00:16:54,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um...</font>

312
00:16:55,680 --> 00:16:58,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can you not see 
out of your right eye?</font>

313
00:16:59,400 --> 00:17:00,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, yeah.</font>

314
00:17:00,350 --> 00:17:01,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Haven't I mentioned it?</font>

315
00:17:01,690 --> 00:17:04,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a false eye, 
so I can't see out of it.</font>

316
00:17:06,370 --> 00:17:08,330
<font size="20" color="#000000"><b><font face="Georgia"><font size="25"><font color="#362016">Sakura Room</font></font></font></b></font>

317
00:17:08,760 --> 00:17:12,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you know about Siu-san's right eye?</font>

318
00:17:12,040 --> 00:17:15,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There were some times when 
I thought it might be, but...</font>

319
00:17:15,440 --> 00:17:17,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I never heard anything in particular.</font>

320
00:17:17,180 --> 00:17:19,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, that figures.</font>

321
00:17:19,120 --> 00:17:21,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He seems like he'd tell 
us if we asked, but...</font>

322
00:17:21,430 --> 00:17:24,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's hard to broach the topic, right?</font>

323
00:17:24,670 --> 00:17:27,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. And it seems like 
a lot happened, so...</font>

324
00:17:28,220 --> 00:17:30,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sero-san seems like he'd know, though.</font>

325
00:17:32,610 --> 00:17:37,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why Sero-san is 
always on Siu-san's left side!</font>

326
00:17:39,390 --> 00:17:44,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Love really does hide in the nooks 
and crannies of everyday life, huh?</font>

327
00:17:44,100 --> 00:17:45,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What does that mean?</font>

328
00:17:47,190 --> 00:17:48,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well...</font>

329
00:17:48,630 --> 00:17:50,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll write about it in a novel one day!</font>

330
00:17:51,360 --> 00:17:54,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really? I look forward to 
the day when I can read it!</font>

331
00:17:56,960 --> 00:17:58,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks!</font>

332
00:18:29,920 --> 00:18:32,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you see something cool 
out there or something?</font>

333
00:18:32,370 --> 00:18:34,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh. Did I wake you?</font>

334
00:18:35,800 --> 00:18:36,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not really.</font>

335
00:18:38,000 --> 00:18:40,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So why are you sitting 
here alone, lost in thought?</font>

336
00:18:41,000 --> 00:18:42,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did I look like a stunning picture?</font>

337
00:18:42,960 --> 00:18:43,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ugh.</font>

338
00:18:46,160 --> 00:18:48,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was just thinking 
that it's a nice place.</font>

339
00:18:49,680 --> 00:18:52,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. The scenery's nice.</font>

340
00:18:52,050 --> 00:18:53,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not that.</font>

341
00:18:54,670 --> 00:18:56,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm talking about Spirytus.</font>

342
00:18:59,840 --> 00:19:03,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've wandered in and out 
of a lot of different jobs.</font>

343
00:19:04,460 --> 00:19:07,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's kind of a mystery to me 
how I've stayed here this long.</font>

344
00:19:09,380 --> 00:19:12,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And it makes me wonder 
how long I'll be able to stay.</font>

345
00:19:14,240 --> 00:19:18,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can stay forever. 
You're needed, after all.</font>

346
00:19:19,330 --> 00:19:21,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can stay for as long as you want to.</font>

347
00:19:21,930 --> 00:19:22,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Actually...</font>

348
00:19:23,200 --> 00:19:25,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">stay to make things easier for me.</font>

349
00:19:30,190 --> 00:19:31,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In that case,</font>

350
00:19:31,330 --> 00:19:35,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">for the company, society, and you, 
I'd better give it my best.</font>

351
00:19:35,470 --> 00:19:37,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It sounds so flippant when you say it.</font>

352
00:19:37,530 --> 00:19:38,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

353
00:19:39,260 --> 00:19:40,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you know...</font>

354
00:19:40,520 --> 00:19:43,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that lightheartedness is 
one of your good points.</font>

355
00:19:45,760 --> 00:19:48,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mike asked me about my eye.</font>

356
00:19:48,370 --> 00:19:49,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He did?</font>

357
00:19:50,440 --> 00:19:53,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, he didn't ask for details.</font>

358
00:19:54,730 --> 00:19:58,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I wouldn't mind 
telling those guys about it.</font>

359
00:19:59,480 --> 00:20:01,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's fine to take it slow, I think.</font>

360
00:20:02,190 --> 00:20:04,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's still a bunch of stuff 
even I don't know.</font>

361
00:20:08,030 --> 00:20:10,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll wait until you're ready 
to talk about it.</font>

362
00:20:11,040 --> 00:20:13,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It'll probably take years.</font>

363
00:20:15,980 --> 00:20:19,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then I ask for your continued 
good will for many years to come.</font>

364
00:20:19,220 --> 00:20:20,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I, the same.</font>

365
00:20:39,780 --> 00:20:41,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Morning!</font>

366
00:20:41,500 --> 00:20:43,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good morning!</font>

367
00:20:43,660 --> 00:20:45,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you guys doing here so early?</font>

368
00:20:46,950 --> 00:20:49,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're doing some torture studies.</font>

369
00:20:49,560 --> 00:20:54,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We want to get better at torturing, 
like you and Siu-san.</font>

370
00:20:54,750 --> 00:20:55,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right?</font>

371
00:20:56,940 --> 00:20:58,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I like that attitude.</font>

372
00:21:00,440 --> 00:21:03,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I read that one, too! 
That brings back memories!</font>

373
00:21:04,280 --> 00:21:07,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The exercises in this book 
are really hard.</font>

374
00:21:07,860 --> 00:21:10,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, yeah, those. These are—</font>

375
00:21:11,560 --> 00:21:13,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are you dawdling in here?</font>

376
00:21:13,480 --> 00:21:14,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Siu-san?</font>

377
00:21:14,800 --> 00:21:17,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Didn't you get the message I just sent?</font>

378
00:21:17,110 --> 00:21:19,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We picked up an urgent case.</font>

379
00:21:19,370 --> 00:21:23,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Since he's tough to deal with, 
they wanted Spirytus to take him.</font>

380
00:21:23,760 --> 00:21:26,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And that's why you're all coming, too.</font>

381
00:21:26,900 --> 00:21:27,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, sir!</font>

382
00:21:30,390 --> 00:21:32,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, shall we get started?</font>

383
00:21:32,800 --> 00:21:34,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay!</font>

384
00:21:34,140 --> 00:21:35,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm ready anytime.</font>

385
00:21:39,700 --> 00:21:43,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is a highly rare 
four-man special course.</font>

386
00:21:47,890 --> 00:21:51,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, why don't you hurry up 
and spill what you know?</font>

387
00:21:56,880 --> 00:21:59,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Torture Outsourcing Firm Spirytus.</i></font>

388
00:22:00,080 --> 00:22:02,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Today, for the sake of 
a bright, cheerful world...</i></font>

389
00:22:03,490 --> 00:22:05,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I will once again devote myself 
to my part-time torturing!</i></font>

390
